1. *Shvaćam* da ću morati da se prilagodim.(I understand that I will have to adapt.)
2. Šta ti *shvaćaš* od toga? (What do you understand from that?)
3. *Shvatila* sam da je to bila greška.(I realized that it was a mistake.)
4. Ovde treba da *shvatimo* da nam niko ne pomaže.(We need to understand here that nobody is helping us.)
5. *Shvatio* sam da nikad neću biti uspešan. (I understood that I will never be successful.)